# name: Set color of thernal ellipsoids. The PDB must have anisotopic temperature factors. See https://pymolwiki.org/index.php/Color_Values for the PyMOL colors.
# group: pymolpy-MolecularRepresentation
# key: ellipcol
# --
cmd.do("set ellipsoid_color, ${1:red};")
$0
